Music is not paused / muted when window is deactivate / minimized on desktop application. It is a general requirement that the game should pause / mute the audio when minimized. 

Looks like a bug, but I found no code for that LwjglApplication, so it could be intentional. No flags in LwjglApplicationConfiguration seems to be responsible for that. The same behavior was noticed in #1263 but was not answered.

